    "body" : "<p><strong>First Question</strong>: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/508665/difference-between-parseint-and-valueof-in-java\">Difference between parseInt and valueOf in java?</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Second Question</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>NumberFormat format = NumberFormat.getInstance(Locale.FRANCE);\nNumber number = format.parse(\"1,234\");\ndouble d = number.doubleValue();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Third Question</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>DecimalFormat df = new DecimalFormat();\nDecimalFormatSymbols symbols = new DecimalFormatSymbols();\nsymbols.setDecimalSeparator('.');\nsymbols.setGroupingSeparator(',');\ndf.setDecimalFormatSymbols(symbols);\ndf.parse(p);\n</code></pre>\n"
