      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Thanks for this. I was using Integer.valueOf and getting a NullPointerException when pulling an int from a database and trying to convert it from String to int in Java. NOT String to Integer. I had to switch to Integer.parseInt() instead."
